data.description: New kitchen installed October/November 2023! This home is interesting and unique, it features; 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2+ living spaces, 2 dining spaces, bonus reading/4th bedroom space, etc, etc... ROOF and 3 SKYLIGHTS replaced 12/2022… hurricane impact windows - 2018... older AC but works great! These sellers have multiple exterior sitting/entertaining spaces... front, side and back yard entertaining for the outdoor persons. Seller has lived in this home for approx 22 years, they have taken great care and have updated thru-out the years and made comfortable for their taste. The home is huge, over 2100sf heated  and has multiple rooms thru out with many possibilities, most rooms have wall to wall closets, providing for lots of storage space...  The kitchen is large, seller took off the market to put new kitchen in, newer stainless appliances, with eat-in space and a large pantry, with custom ceiling that has access to a spacious attic. The back Family room is very spacious, insulated, but not under AC, sellers used to house a full size pool table, but recently, they sectioned off a 10x8 room within this Florida room with temporary walls to make a 4th bedroom/hang out room for the grandkids, there is a wall unit, but not included in the heated sf (no closet). The Master bedroom is at the back of the home for a true split floor plan, it has a large walk-in closet, not currently being used as a closet. Again, this home has many possibilities, great space, and not too much to do to make this your own space. ONLY 6 miles from the BEACH... short distanced to the Pinellas Trail... Seminole Rec Center... Churches... Restaurants... Largo Mall +... etc! Make your appt today!
